title: Jackie 2012 DVDRip Sonata Premiere
description:
Twin sisters - a prim, ambitious magazine editor (Carice van Houten, HBO's "Game of Thrones") and a warm, family-oriented housewife (real-life sibling Jelka van Houten) - travel to the American Southwest in search of the biological mother they've never met (Academy Award winner Holly Hunter). Finding her the worse for wear and living out of a battered RV, they drive their mother cross-state to a rehab center on a journey that will redefine the meaning of "family" for all of them. With beautiful cinematography, shot on location in the breathtaking desert landscapes of New Mexico, JACKIE is a fresh and heartwarming take on the classic American road movie. (c) Tribeca
